 on a variety of tricep exercises that hit all three tricep heads for comprehensive and balanced development.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/tricep-workouts-for-beginners#faq-question-1729508386147","position":3,"url":"https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/tricep-workouts-for-beginners#faq-question-1729508386147","name":"How often should I train my triceps?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The frequency of training your triceps depends on your goals and fitness level. Beginners should aim for 2–3 tricep workouts per week, allowing time for other workouts that focus on other upper-body muscles.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/tricep-workouts-for-beginners#faq-question-1729508411240","position":4,"url":"https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/tricep-workouts-for-beginners#faq-question-1729508411240","name":"Do training triceps make the arms bigger?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Training your triceps using resistance exercises like the ones listed is effective at inducing muscle breakdown to rebuild them stronger. These workouts provide a valuable stimulus that will enhance muscle growth for bigger arms.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/tricep-workouts-for-beginners#faq-question-1729508427944","position":5,"url":"https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/tricep-workouts-for-beginners#faq-question-1729508427944","name":"How long does it take to see results from tricep training?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The amount of time to see results from weight training depends on factors such as age, gender, and fitness level. However, it generally takes 4–6 weeks to begin seeing progress from resistance training. By following a structured plan with consistency, you will maximize your gains.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/tricep-workouts-for-beginners#faq-question-1729508439867","position":6,"url":"https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/tricep-workouts-for-beginners#faq-question-1729508439867","name":"Can I train my triceps at home without equipment?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"There are multiple exercises designed for training triceps at home without equipment. Some of the ones we’ve described above only require bodyweight, making them very accessible for at-home workouts. The chair tricep dip and push-up are both great options.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"}]}</script>
